You need to build a complete Blazor Static SSR university course catalog app. The project is at `/tmp/sv-dd541ae49e5e4ca8a44e2e8a531d821b/UniversityCourseCatalog`.

Here's what exists already:
- Standard blazor template with Components/Pages (Home.razor, Weather.razor, Error.razor, NotFound.razor), Components/Layout (MainLayout.razor, NavMenu.razor, NavMenu.razor.css, NavMenu.razor.js), Components/App.razor, Components/Routes.razor, Components/_Imports.razor
- Program.cs (basic, no services registered)
- wwwroot/app.css (template defaults)

## Steps to complete (do ALL of these):

### 1. Create Models directory and files

Create `UniversityCourseCatalog/Models/Department.cs`:
```csharp
namespace UniversityCourseCatalog.Models;

